rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Mathias about Primordia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Mathias about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Mathias about Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Mathias about Noctilum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0001
rows.name:
After Aisha came back the other day, I gave her a
collar that contains a small camera.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0002
rows.name:
One of the images it collected was of New LA,
but taken from an unbelievably high position.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0003
rows.name:
It looks like it was from somewhere just north of the
city. I didn't know you could even get up that high.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0004
rows.name:
If I get any more interesting pictures back from her,
I'll let you know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0008
rows.name:
You can now keep pet dogs, as well as cats made
from Aisha's biological data, in your rooms at the
BLADE barracks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0009
rows.name:
To be clear, they're just mimeosomes,
not real animals like Aisha.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0010
rows.name: Even so, it's still pretty great to have a pet.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0011
rows.name:
But I recently had a few escape on me.
I was just heading out to post the search request at
Mission Control.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0012
rows.name:
If you complete the mission, I'll give you a mimeosome
pet on the house! So if that sort of thing interests you,
please accept the job.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0017
rows.name: The camera collar on Aisha caught a really rare sight![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0018
rows.name:
It seems to be a Prone village, probably somewhere
in Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0019
rows.name:
And it looks like a Prone woman is actually giving
Aisha food![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0020
rows.name:
The Prone's face has a peaceful expression that they
don't reveal to us humans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0021
rows.name:
I mean, that's the impression I get, anyway.
But I wouldn't bet the house on it or anything.
You know how their faces are.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0026
rows.name:
I got some interesting pictures back from the camera
collar around Aisha's neck.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0027
rows.name:
I think they were taken near the Canopied Nightwood
in Noctilum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0028
rows.name:
It looks like the boulder Aisha was napping on was
actually a camouflaged falsaxum![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0029
rows.name: I was terrified that she'd end up being eaten alive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0030
rows.name:
But it looks like Aisha took it down with a vicious flurry
of cat punches and kitty kicks![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0031
rows.name:
...What? Aisha is an accomplished BLADE.
She's a member of the tyrant-hunting Harriers division.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0036
rows.name:
It was never part of the plan to have Aisha aboard
the White Whale.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0037
rows.name:
They figured that transporting simple genetic data from
animals would have to be sufficient.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0038
rows.name:
But amidst the chaos surrounding the launch,
Aisha managed to sneak into the engine room.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0039
rows.name:
I was the one who discovered her there. I told Gwin,
then we reported it to Commander Vandham.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0040
rows.name:
We thought he'd be angry, but he gave us permission
to keep her! He said cats have ridden on ships as
good-luck charms since ancient times.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0041
rows.name:
There weren't any rats to hunt on the White Whale,
but she did good work keeping up morale.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0042
rows.name:
Oh, if we're talking cars, I'm going with a sports car
all the way.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0043
rows.name:
Sure, they may not have the horsepower necessary
to drive around on the untamed plains of Mira...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0044
rows.name:
But that beautiful styling? The smooth sensation of
speed? They personify the soul of the automobile![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0045
rows.name:
Oh, hi there, [ST:playername ]! Gwin and I
were just discussing our favorite automobiles.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0046
rows.name:
If you don't mind sharing, I'd love to hear what kind
of car gets your heart racing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0047
rows.name:
I came here because Gwin offered to treat me to a
decent meal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0048
rows.name:
But it's pretty clear that I was summoned so those two
wouldn't have to be alone together.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016701_MSG0049
rows.name:
Next time, I've got to remember to ask who else is
coming before I accept. This isn't helping Gwin at all![ST:wait ]
